<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Airpods on ittechnetworkk</title><link>https://ittechnetworkk.github.io/tags/airpods/</link><description>Recent content in Airpods on ittechnetworkk</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><copyright>ittechnetworkk</copyright><lastBuildDate>Sun, 31 Aug 2025 03:58:55 +0200</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ittechnetworkk.github.io/tags/airpods/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Airpods in linux</title><link>https://ittechnetworkk.github.io/posts/airpodsinlinux/airpodsinlinux/</link><pubDate>Sun, 31 Aug 2025 03:58:55 +0200</pubDate><guid>https://ittechnetworkk.github.io/posts/airpodsinlinux/airpodsinlinux/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Selamlar! Bu yazıda AirPods&amp;rsquo;u Linux&amp;rsquo;ta nasıl kullanabileceğimizden kısaca bahsedeceğim.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;/etc/bluetooth/main.conf&lt;/code&gt; dosyasına aşağıdaki satırı eklemeniz veya varsa aşağıdaki şekilde düzeltmeniz işi çözecektir:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#8be9fd;font-style:italic"&gt;ControllerMode&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; bredr
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Daha sonra Bluetooth ile tekrar bir tarama yaparsanız, Linux cihazınız AirPods&amp;rsquo;u görecektir.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Not:&lt;/strong&gt; Değişikliklerin etkili olması için Bluetooth servisini yeniden başlatmanız gerekebilir:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo systemctl restart bluetooth
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Teşekkürler,&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;İyi çalışmalar.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>